Merrill Lynch Canada, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 21, 2017 3:25 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Merrill Lynch Canada, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Merrill Lynch Canada, Inc. is a global corporate and investment banking firm. The firm offers commercial lending, global high-yield debt, global equity, and global mergers and acquisitions services. It also offers brokerage and investment banking services, including capital raising, debt financing, risk management, mortgage lending, equity research, underwriting, equity sales and trading, and strategic advisory. It caters to corporate, institutional, and government clients. The firm was founded in 1952 and is based in Toronto, Canada with additional offices in Montreal, Calgary, and Vancouver. Merrill Lynch Canada, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Merrill Lynch & Co., Canada Ltd.


BCE PlaceWellington Tower181 Bay Street4th and 5th FloorsToronto, ON M5J 2V8CanadaFounded in 1952



Phone: 416-369-7400

Fax: 416-369-7966

www.invest.baml.com/ca/en-GB







