Branch Office Profile

The Merrill Lynch Menlo Park Office is the parent office of the Menlo Park Market. The Market is comprised of three offices, Menlo Park, San Mateo and an office in San Francisco at 101 California Street. Advisors in each of our offices focus on delivering customized wealth management strategies to high net worth individuals and businesses while delivering unsurpassed service.   We pride ourselves in our ability to earn our clients’ trust, and measure our success by the level of confidence our clients have in our abilities. Our primary focus is to go beyond financial advice and help our clients achieve the life they want. Over the years, generations of clients have entrusted us with their financial lives. You can be assured that we have the integrity and record of success you expect from a trusted advisor.  
ABOUT THE MANAGER Michael Ronan has been in the financial services industry since 1983.  He joined Merrill Lynch in 1996 as a Financial Advisor.  Michael accepted a full time position in Management in June of 2008 and was named the Market Executive in Menlo Park in June of 2011. In 2016, Michael was promoted to Managing Director. He has a history of community involvement in San Francisco.  Michael is on the Advisory Board for National Foundation for Teaching Entrepreneurship and a mentor with Achieve, a San Francisco based non-profit.  He graduated from California State University San Diego; receiving a Bachelor's degree in Business Administration with a concentration in Finance.  Michael and his wife Maha have been married since 1993.








